<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>About - Game Shop</title>
    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/about.css" /> <!-- 外部 CSS 文件 -->
</head>

<body class="background d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
    <%- include('../components/navbar.ejs') %>
    <%- include('../components/alertBlock.ejs') %> <!-- 添加警报组件，与其他页面保持一致 -->

    <div class="container-fluid mt-4 mx-auto w-75">
        <h1 class="display-4">About Game Shop</h1>

        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <h4>Our Story</h4>
                <p>
                    Welcome to Game Shop, your ultimate destination for gaming adventures! We started with a passion for bringing the best games to players worldwide. Our journey began with a small team of enthusiasts who wanted to create a space where gamers could find their next favorite title, from action-packed shooters to immersive RPGs. Today, we’re proud to offer a curated selection of games, backed by a community of dedicated players and developers.
                </p>
                <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide w-75 h-50 mx-auto d-none d-lg-block" data-ride="carousel" aria-label="Game Shop Highlights">
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="/public/assets/storefront.jpg" alt="Game Shop storefront">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="/public/assets/team.jpg" alt="Our gaming team">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="/public/assets/community.jpg" alt="Gaming community event">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid mt-2">
            <div class="container">
                <h4>Our Lead Developer</h4>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Meet Alex, our visionary lead developer who’s been shaping the gaming world for over a decade. With a knack for crafting unforgettable experiences, Alex has worked on some of the biggest titles in the industry before joining Game Shop. Passionate about innovation and player satisfaction, Alex ensures every game we offer meets the highest standards of quality and fun.
                </p>
                <div class="container-fluid w-50 d-none d-lg-block">
                    <img class="img-thumbnail d-block w-100" src="/public/assets/lead-developer.jpg" alt="Alex, our lead developer" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>